            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">Naomi Levine came to New York University in 1980. She became the Vice President of External Affairs and led a $2 billion dollar fundraising campaign in her 22 years of service. The following collection includes some of her correspondences and papers relating to the Office of External Affairs.</abstract>
